A fashion and jewellery showcase by Joo & Co and Kache by Angie Designs was recently held at the Norfolk Hotel Nairobi. The event was part of the Norfolk arts series, meant to provide artistes with a platform to showcase and display their works. Joo & Company, a Nairobi-based designer, showcased their exquisite, modern yet timeless jewellery collection. Kache, on the other hand, is a high-end fashion business operated by a Spanish-born entrepreneur, Angie Messeguer. It showcased classy and stylish outfit collections from Barcelona, Spain, which have carved a niche in the market.